Exception : gradle task assembledebug failed with exit code 1

---------------
When : try to build

How to solve this problem :
--> uninstall The Latest version - 'NDK (Side by side)' (at Setting - Android SDK - SDK Tools). // EX) ver.23
--> install previous version - 'NDK (Side by side)' // EX) ver.22


